#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about calm consequences.\n"
"\n"
"Our actions have consequences. Some consequences happen naturally (“if you break something, you can’t use it anymore”). Other consequences we set as a family to motivate us to follow the rules (“if you come home late, you can’t go out with friends tomorrow”).\n"
"\n"
"HOW you set and use consequences together matters.\n"
"\n"
"Getting consequences right helps teens behave better and makes family life calmer."
msgstr ""
"Mada ya leo ni kuhusu athari nyepesi.\n"
"\n"
"Matendo yetu yana matokeo. Baadhi ya matokeo hutokea kwa kawaida (“kama ukivunja kitu, huwezi kukitumia tena”). Athari nyepesi zingine tunaweka kama familia ili kutuhamasisha kufuata sheria (“kama ukirudi nyumbani ukiwa umechelewa, hautaruhusiwa kutoka na marafiki kesho”).\n"
"\n"
"JINSI unavyoweka na kutumia adhabu nyepesi pamoja ni muhimu.\n"
"\n"
"Kuweka matokeo ipasavyo husaidia vijana kuenenda vyema na hufanya maisha ya familia kuwa na utulivu zaidi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How will introducing calm consequences help you and your family? Play to learn more"
msgstr "Je, kuanzisha adhabu nyepesi kutasaidia vipi wewe na familia yako? Bonyeza ili ujifunze zaidi\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is calm consequences.\n"
"\n"
"It is important that when we introduce consequences to our teenagers we involve them, but also important that we are calm when we introduce consequences.\n"
"\n"
"That will assist us to agree on introducing calm consequences to our teenagers, and our teenagers will easily remember them when they are involved and that will make them responsible."
msgstr ""
"Habari, zetu.\n"
"\n"
"Mada ya leo ni athari nyepesi.\n"
"\n"
"Ni muhimu kwamba tunapoanzisha adhabu nyepesi kwa vijana wetu tuwahusishe, lakini pia ni muhimu tuwe na utulivu tunapowasilisha adhabu hizo.\n"
"\n"
"Hilo litatusaidia kukubaliana kuhusu kuanzisha adhabu nyepesi kwa vijana wetu, na vijana wetu watazikumbuka kwa urahisi wanapohusishwa, na hilo litawafanya kuwa wa kuwajibika.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Calm consequences work best when they are fair, agreed on together, and followed through consistently - not in anger."
msgstr "Adhabu nyepesi hufanya kazi vizuri zaidi  zikiwa za haki, kwa kukubaliana pamoja, na kufuatwa kwa uthabiti — si kwa hasira."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_13.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Agreeing on consequences together works! Tap play to hear @data.characters.media_female_13.name tell her story"
msgstr "Kukubaliana juu ya adhabu nyepesi pamoja hufanya kazi! Bonyeza cheza kusikiliza  @data.characters.media_female_13.name msimulie hadithi\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When my teenagers did something to make me angry, I would shout at them and punish them right away. But the next time they did it again! I could not understand why they did not hear me even when I shouted.\n"
"\n"
"@global.app_name helped me understand that my teenagers will listen to me more when I am calm. So, when something happens, I take a deep breath and say “we will talk about this later when we are both calm.”\n"
"\n"
"We even agree on the consequences together now before something goes wrong. This has worked wonders – I have seen a huge change in my teen’s behaviour now that they are more involved, and I have less stress.\n"
"\n"
"I wish I knew this long ago, but it is never too late to start!"
msgstr ""
"Wakati vijana wangu walipofanya jambo lililonikasirisha, nilikuwa nikiwapigia kelele na kuwaadhibu mara moja. Lakini wakati nyingine walilifanya tena! Sikuweza kuelewa kwa nini hawakunielewa hata nilipopaza sauti.\n"
"\n"
"@global.app_name imenisaidia kuelewa kwamba vijana wangu watanisikiliza zaidi ninapokuwa mtulivu. Hivyo basi, jambo fulani linapotokea, huchukua pumzi ndefu na kusema, “tutazungumza kuhusu hili baadaye tukishatulia wote wawili.”\n"
"\n"
"Hata sasa tunakubaliana kuhusu athari nyepesi pamoja kabla jambo halijaharibika. Hii imeleta mafanikio makubwa – nimeona mabadiliko makubwa katika tabia ya kijana wangu sasa kwamba anahusishwa zaidi, na nina msongo mdogo wa mawazo.\n"
"\n"
"Natamani ningejua haya zamani, lakini  bado sijachelewa kuanza!."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name:
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's read what happened with @data.characters.f1_son_18.name and his father, @data.characters.f1_father.name:"
msgstr "Acha tusome kile kilichotokea kwa @data.characters.f1_son_18.name na baba yake, @data.characters.f1_father.name:"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name! What time is this? You are late!"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name! Huu ni muda gani? Umechelewa!\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name, you broke our rule! I will give you a hiding!"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name, umevunja sheria yetu! Nitakuchapa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s unfair! You never listen to me!! I hate you!"
msgstr "Hii sio sawa! Haunisikilizi!! Nakuchukia!\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's think about what happened in this story."
msgstr "Hebu tufikirie kuhusu kilichotokea kwenye hadithi hii."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why did giving a consequence this way not work well?"
msgstr "Je, kwa nini amri ya kufanya athari kwa njia hii haikufanikiwa vizuri?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name was angry"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name alikua na hasira\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name did not let his son, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, explain"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name  hakumruhusu mtoto wake, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, elezea\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The consequence was not discussed beforehand with @data.characters.f1_son_18.name"
msgstr "Matokeo hayakujadiliwa mapema na @data.characters.f1_son_18.name\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The consequence was too strong"
msgstr "Athari ilikuwa ngumu mno"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, a strong reaction like that just made everyone more angry and upset."
msgstr "Ndiyo, mwitikio mkubwa kama huo ulimfanya kila mtu kukasirika zaidi na kusikitika."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Teens often break rules. This is normal - growing up is a difficult time when they are learning about who they are.\n"
"\n"
"Luckily, there are ways to discipline without getting angry or using violence… and they work well!\n"
"\n"
"Giving calm consequences is important because it helps teens learn from their actions and take responsibility for their choices."
msgstr ""
"Vijana mara nyingi huvunja sheria. Hii ni kawaida – kukua ni kipindi kigumu wanapojifunza kuhusu wao ni nani.\n"
"\n"
"Kwa bahati nzuri, kuna njia za kujenga nidhamu bila hasira wala kutumia vurugu… na zinafanya kazi vizuri!\n"
"\n"
"Kutoa adhabu nyepesi ni muhimu kwa sababu inawasaidia vijana kujifunza kutokana na matendo yao na kuwajibika kwa maamuzi wanayofanya."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Imagine you are the parent and @data.characters.f1_son_18.name came home late. \n"
"What consequence would help here?"
msgstr ""
"Fikiria  kwamba wewe ni mzazi na @data.characters.f1_son_18.name  amerudi nyumbani amechelewa. \n"
"Adhabu gani nyepesi ingeweza kusaidia hapa?\n"
"\n"
"\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cannot play with phone the next day"
msgstr "Hataweza kuchezea simu siku inayofuata\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That's right!\n"
"\n"
"And remember, consequences are not quite the same as punishment: they give our teens a chance to learn responsibility for their actions.\n"
"\n"
"And they are more controlled AND effective than hitting or shouting!"
msgstr ""
"Hiyo ni sahihi!\n"
"\n"
"Na kumbuka, athari nyepesi si sawa kabisa na adhabu: yanawapa vijana wetu nafasi ya kujifunza kuwajibika kwa matendo yao.\n"
"\n"
"Na ni rahisi zaidi kudhibitiwa na zina ufanisi kuliko kupiga au kupiga kelele!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Now imagine @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name and @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name fight over a phone. \n"
"What consequence would help here?"
msgstr ""
"Sasa fikiri @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name na @data.characters.f1_daughter_13.name wanagombania. \n"
"Ni athari gani nyepesi zitasaidia hapa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No gadget use the next day"
msgstr "Hakuna kutumia vifaa vya kielektroniki siku inayofuata"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Write a letter of apology"
msgstr "Kuandika barua ya kuomba msamaha"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cannot see friends the next day"
msgstr "Haruhusiwi kuwatembelea marafiki siku inayofuata"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cannot play with phone after dinner (or next hour)"
msgstr "Haruhusiwi kuchezea simu baada ya chakula cha usiku (au saa inayofuata)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Take 5 minutes' pause in a separate part of the room"
msgstr "Kutulia kwa dakika 5 ukiwa upande mwingine wa chumba"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great idea! Calm consequences work best when they are fair, happen soon after the behaviour, and are used the same way each time. This helps your teen understand what to expect and gives them a clear chance to learn from their actions."
msgstr "Wazo zuri! Athari nyepesi zinafanya kazi vyema zaidi zinapokuwa za haki, zinapotokea mara moja baada ya tabia hiyo, na zinapotumika kwa njia ile ile kila wakati. Hii humsaidia kijana wako kuelewa kile anachopaswa kutarajia na huwapa nafasi ya wazi ya kujifunza kutokana na matendo yao."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_15.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Now imagine @data.characters.f2_son_15.name is helping with a special chore. \n"
"What consequence would help here?"
msgstr ""
"Sasa fikiria @data.characters.f2_son_15.name anasaidia kazi maalumu. \n"
"Ni athari gani nyepesi ingeweza kusaidia hapa?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Extra time with friends on weekend (1 hr)"
msgstr "Muda wa ziada wa kuungana na marafiki wikiendi (saa 1)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cooking teen's favourite meal"
msgstr "Kupika chakula pendwa cha kijana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Extra time with phone after dinner (30 min)"
msgstr "Muda wa ziada akiwa na simu baada ya chakula cha usiku (dakika 30)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Watching teen's TV show together"
msgstr ""
"Kutazama kipindi cha televisheni cha kijana pamoja.\n"
"Kutaza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Extra one-on-one time on Sunday (30 min)"
msgstr "Muda wa ziada wa kuzungumza wawili Jumapili (dakika 30)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Wonderful! Positive consequences like this build trust and show your teen that helpful behaviour is noticed and appreciated. When rewards are fair, timely, and consistent, they motivate teens to keep making good choices and strengthen your bond too."
msgstr "Nzuri sana! Matokeo chanya kama haya hujenga uaminifu na kuonyesha kwa kijana wako kwamba tabia nzuri inatambuliwa na kuthaminiwa. Pale zawadi  ni zahaki, kwa wakati muafaka, na kwa uthabiti, huwawezesha vijana kuendelea kufanya maamuzi mazuri na pia huimarisha uhusiano wenu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some tips to help you with calm consequences:"
msgstr "Hapa kuna vidokezo kadhaa vya kukusaidia kwenye athari nyepesi:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "EXPLAIN"
msgstr "ELEZA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Check you are both calm. Take a few breaths. Explain to your teen why you are concerned about their behaviour.\n"
"\n"
"Explain the reasons why the rule mattered. You can share your feelings – it is okay to say you are disappointed."
msgstr ""
"Hakikisha wote wawili mmetulia. Vuta pumzi mara kadhaa. Mweleze kijana wako kwa nini una wasiwasi na tabia zake.\n"
"\n"
"Eleza kwa nini sheria hiyo ilikuwa muhimu. Unaweza kumshirikisha hisia zako – si vibaya kusema umesikitika."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How you introduce calm consequences is important. When you involve your teen, things usually go better!"
msgstr "Jinsi unavyowasilisha athari nyepesi ni muhimu. Unapomhusisha kijana wako, mambo mara nyingi huenda vizuri zaidi!\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "AGREE"
msgstr "KUBALI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Plan consequences with your teen for following and not following the rule.\n"
"\n"
"Ask for their ideas. Talk until you agree on something realistic.\n"
"\n"
"Make a consequence for NOT following the rule and a privilege when they DO follow the rule."
msgstr ""
"Panga na kijana wako athari za kufuata sheria na kutofuata sheria.\n"
"\n"
"Mwombe atoe maoni yake. Zungumzeni hadi mtakapokubaliana kuhusu kitu halisi.\n"
"\n"
"Weka athari za KUTOFUATA sheria na upendeleo pindi WANAPOFUATA sheria."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, consequences are more successful if you discuss and agree in advance with teens before you apply them."
msgstr "Kumbuka, matokeo huwa na mafanikio zaidi ikiwa utajadili na kukubaliana na vijana mapema kabla ya kuyatekeleza.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "ACT"
msgstr "TENDA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**When your teen follows the rule, give praise and privileges!** \n"
"They will feel respected and valued. Remember: The more we praise them, the more they will show that good behaviour!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"**When your teen does not follow the rule, follow through with the consequence.** \n"
"When your teen breaks the rule, calmly give the consequence. This should be FAIR (not too harsh), IMMEDIATE (do it straight away), CONSISTENT (same every time)."
msgstr ""
"**Wakati kijana wako anapofuata kanuni, msifie na mpe nafsi ya pekee!**\n"
"Wataona kuwa wanaheshimiwa na kuthaminiwa. Kumbuka: Kadri tunavyowasifia zaidi, ndivyo wanavyoendelea kuonyesha tabia njema!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"**Kijana wako anapokiuka kanuni, tekeleza athari iliyokubaliwa.**\n"
"Wakati kijana wako anapovunja kanuni, toa adhabu nyepesi kwa utulivu. Hii inapaswa kuwa YA HAKI (si kali kupita kiasi), YA HARAKA (itekelezwe mara moja), THABITI (iwe hivyo kila mara)."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Vidokezo zaidi\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, you can also agree on GOOD consequences for GOOD actions to see more positive behaviour!"
msgstr "Kumbuka, pia mnaweza kukubaliana juu ya matokeo MAZURI kwa matendo MAZURI ili kuona tabia chanya zaidi!\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name:
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now let's go back to @data.characters.f1_son_18.name and his father, @data.characters.f1_father.name:"
msgstr "Acha tuangalie tena @data.characters.f1_son_18.name na baba yake, @data.characters.f1_father.name:\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am concerned that you are often still coming home late, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. What can we do to help you remember to come home in time?"
msgstr "Ninatiwa wasiwasi kwamba bado unachelewa kurudi nyumbani mara kwa mara,  @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. Je tunaweza kufanya nini kukusaidia ukumbuke kurudi nyumbani kwa wakati?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "If I come home in time, maybe I can stay up 30 minutes later than usual?"
msgstr "Je kama nitarudi nyumbani kwa wakati, labda naweza kukaa kwa dakika 30 zaidi kuliko kawaida?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That is a good idea! And what should we do if you don’t follow the rule?"
msgstr "Hilo ni wazo zuri! Na tufanye nini ikiwa hautafuata kanuni?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "(mumbles) Mgmluuhm..."
msgstr "(Anong'ona) Mgmluuhm...\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oh come on, I know you have some ideas."
msgstr "Acha bwana, najua una mawazo fulani.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay…. What about, I have to do my homework?"
msgstr "Sawa… Na je, lazima nifanye kazi ya nyumbani?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You have to do your homework anyway. If you forget the rule, is it fair that you will not be able to see your friends the next day?"
msgstr "Lazima ufanye kazi yako ya nyumbani hata hivyo. Ukisahau kanuni, je, ni haki kwamba hutakuwa na ruhusa ya kuwaona marafiki zako siku inayofuata?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name."
msgstr "Sawa,  @data.characters.f1_father.role_name.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*The next day...*"
msgstr "*Siku inayofuata...*"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name! What time is it! It is late!"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name! Sasa hivi ni  saa ngapi! Umechelewa!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sorry @data.characters.f1_father.role_name – you can go back to sleep."
msgstr "Samahani @data.characters.f1_father.role_name – Unaweza kurudi kulala.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is WAY past the time you were supposed to be home!"
msgstr "Umepita sana muda uliotakiwa kuwa nyumbani!\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I can explain, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name, I can."
msgstr "Naweza kuelezea, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name, naweza.\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name,
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name, it is the middle of the night and you came home later than we agreed. Whatever the reason is, you must understand that this is not acceptable. Your @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name and I felt really worried."
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_son_18.name, Ni usiku wa manane na umerudi nyumbani umechelewa kuliko tulivyokubaliana. Hata uwe na sababu yoyote ile, ni lazima uelewe kuwa hili halikubaliki. Yako @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name na nilihisi wasiwasi sana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "My friends wanted me to stay longer. They were calling me a baby for having to go home already."
msgstr "Marafiki zangu walitaka nibaki kwa muda mrefu zaidi. Walikuwa wananitania kwa kuniita mtoto kwa kurudi nyumbani mapema."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I know it can be hard to say no to your friends. Let’s talk more about this in the morning when we have had some rest."
msgstr "Ninajua inaweza kuwa ni vigumu kuwaambia marafiki hapana. Ebu tuzungumze zaidi kuhusu hili asubuhi tutakapokuwa tumepumzika.\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I am sorry I worried you and @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name."
msgstr "Samahani kwa kukusababishia wasiwasi na @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you. Now go to bed, but just to be clear, as you came home later than we agreed, you will not be allowed to go out tomorrow night."
msgstr "Asante. Sasa nenda ukalale, lakini niweke wazi tu, kwa kuwa umerejea nyumbani kwa kuchelewa kuliko tulivyokubaliana, hutoruhusiwa kutoka kesho usiku.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's think about this story."
msgstr "Hebu tufikirie kuhusu hadithi hii."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why did using a consequence work well this time?"
msgstr "Kwa nini amri ya kufanya athari ilifanikiwa vizuri mara hii?"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
