msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name and his son, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, discussed consequences when they were both calm"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name na kijana wake, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, walijadili athari nyepesi  wakati wote wawili wakiwa watulivu\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "They agreed on consequences together"
msgstr "Walikubaliana pamoja kuhusu athari"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name responded calmly but firmly when @data.characters.f1_son_18.name broke the rule"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name alijibu kwa utulivu lakini kwa msimamo thabiti wakati @data.characters.f1_son_18.name amevunja sheria\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name listened to his son"
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.name alimsikiliza mwanae\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "The consequence was realistic and appropriate"
msgstr "Athari ziikuwa sahihi na zinazotekelezeka"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly! Consequences work best when they are set calmly, agreed on together, and followed through with care. By listening to your teen and staying firm but kind, you are correcting behaviour AND building trust and helping them learn responsibility."
msgstr "Kabisa! Athari nyepesi hufanya kazi vyema zaidi yanapowekwa kwa utulivu, kwa makubaliano ya pamoja, na kutekelezwa kwa uangalifu. Kwa kumsikiliza kijana wako na kubaki imara lakini mkarimu, unarekebisha tabia NA pia unajenga uaminifu na kumsaidia kujifunza uwajibikaji.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"It is time to learn and practise!\n"
"\n"
"Plan a calm consequence for your teenagers arguing with each other during dinner."
msgstr ""
"Ni wakati wa kujifunza na kufanyia mazoezi!\n"
"\n"
"Panga athari nyepesi kwa vijana wako  kwa kubishana wao kwa wao wakati wa chakula cha Jioni."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some ideas from other parents. Tap each behaviour to see an example of a fair consequence!"
msgstr "Hapa kuna baadhi ya mawazo kutoka kwa wazazi wengine. Gusa kila tabia kuona mfano mzuri wa athari nyepesi ya haki!\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Negative Behaviour: Coming home after the agreed time"
msgstr "Tabia Hasi: Kurudi nyumbani baada ya muda uliokubaliwa\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Negative Consequence: Cannot see friends the next day."
msgstr "Tokeo Hasi: Hataruhusiwa kuwaona marafiki siku inayofuata.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Negative Behaviour: Talking rudely"
msgstr "Tabia Hasi: Kuzungumza kwa ukatili\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Negative Consequence: Write a letter of apology."
msgstr "Tokeo Hasi: Andika barua ya kuomba msamaha.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Positive Behaviour: Helping out with shopping"
msgstr "Tabia Chanya: Kusaidia katika ununuzi\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Positive Consequence: 30 minutes extra doing an activity of their choice."
msgstr "Tokeo Chanya: Dakika 30 za ziada kufanya shughuli wanayoichagua wenyewe.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Positive Behaviour: Helping look after younger siblings"
msgstr "Tabia Chanya: Kusaidia kuwalea wadogo zako.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Positive Consequence: One hour of extra time with friends on the weekend."
msgstr "Tokeo Chanya: Saa moja ya ziada kutumia muda na marafiki wikendi.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now let's think more about negative consequences. Which of these consequences do you feel is appropriate?"
msgstr "Sasa hebu tufikirie zaidi kuhusu matokeo hasi. Ni ipi kati ya matokeo haya unahisi kuwa inafaa?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Not seeing any friends for a month"
msgstr "Hakuna kumtembelea rafiki yeyote kwa mwezi mmoja"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This may be hard to do for you and also too harsh! \n"
"\n"
"Remember, consequences should be fair, immediate and consistent."
msgstr ""
"Hii inaweza kuwa ngumu kwako kufanya na pia ni kali sana!\n"
"\n"
"Kumbuka, athari nyepesi zinapaswa kuwa za haki, za haraka, na  thabiti."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cancelling their birthday plans in a month's time"
msgstr "Kufuta mipango yao ya siku ya kuzaliwa baada ya mwezi mmoja"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This is too far in the future and too harsh as well! \n"
"\n"
"Remember, consequences should be fair, immediate and consistent."
msgstr ""
"Hii iko mbali sana huko mbele na pia ni kali sana\n"
"\n"
"Kumbuka, athari nyepesi zinapaswa kuwa za haki, za haraka, na  thabiti.\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No TV this evening"
msgstr "Hakuna kuangalia runinga jioni ya leo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Perfect, this sounds fair and can be done straight away."
msgstr "Bora kabisa, ni ya  haki na inaweza kufanyika mara moja."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"It is time to learn and practise!\n"
"\n"
"Your home activity this week is to try using one **positive consequence** when your teen does something well — and one **negative consequence** when they break a household rule."
msgstr ""
"Ni wakati wa kujifunza na kufanyia mazoezi!\n"
"\n"
"Shughuli yako ya nyumbani kwa wiki hii ni kujaribu kutumia **athari chanya** moja wakati kijana wako anapofanya jambo vizuri — na **athari hasi** moja wakati anapovunja sheria ya nyumba."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Remember, consequences should be:** \n"
"⚖️ FAIR (not too harsh) \n"
"💨 IMMEDIATE (do it straight away) \n"
"🎯 CONSISTENT (same every time)"
msgstr ""
"**Kumbuka, athari zinapaswa kuwa:**\n"
"⚖️ HAKI (zisizokali sana)\n"
"💨 ZA HARAKA (zifanyike mara moja)\n"
"🎯 ZA KUDUMU (zisizobadilika kila wakati)"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you agree on one NEGATIVE consequence and one POSITIVE consequence with your teen?"
msgstr "Je, mnaweza kukubaliana na kijana wako kuhusu athari MOJA hasi na athari MOJA chanya?\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ndiyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's fantastic! When teens help choose their own consequences - both positive and negative - they are more likely to understand and stick to them. You are helping them grow into a responsible young adult."
msgstr "Hilo ni jambo zuri sana! Wakati vijana wanaposhirikishwa kuchagua athari zao wenyewe — zote chanya na hasi — huwa wanaelewa zaidi na kuzishika. Unawasaidia kukua na kuwa vijana wawajibikaji."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ninafikiria hivyo\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s a great start! Take your time - you can come up with ideas together step by step."
msgstr "Huo ni mwanzo mzuri! Chukua muda wako — mnaweza kuja na mawazo pamoja hatua kwa hatua."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hapana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. These conversations can be tricky at first. Keep spending time together and try again when the moment feels right. You are already on the right path."
msgstr "Sawa kabisa. Mazungumzo haya yanaweza kuwa magumu mwanzoni. Endeleeni kutumia muda pamoja na jaribu tena wakati ukihisi ni wakati mwafaka. Tayari uko njiani kuelekea kwenye njia sahihi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When consequences are calm, clear, and agreed on together, teens are more likely to follow the rules. They will feel respected, not punished, and that is the best way to help our teens learn."
msgstr "Wakati athari nyepesi zikitolewa kwa utulivu, kwa uwazi, na kwa makubaliano ya pamoja, vijana huwa na uwezekano mkubwa wa kufuata sheria. Watakuwa wakihisi kuheshimiwa badala ya kuadhibiwa — na hiyo ndio njia bora zaidi ya kuwasaidia vijana wetu kujifunza.\n"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_6.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tap play to hear how @data.characters.media_daughter_6.name learned to appreciate calm consequences"
msgstr "Bonyeza ili kusikia ni kwa namna gani @data.characters.media_daughter_6.name  amejifunza kuthamini athari nyepesi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"My mom and dad would always punish me when they were angry with me. They would shout at me and I would also get angry. I often did not follow the rules, because they were too harsh, I did not understand what they were saying, or I would not even bother listening to them, because we were all angry.\n"
"\n"
"One day, they asked me: Let's think together what the consequence should be for not coming home in time. It was great to give my view – before something happens that makes us all angry. We are all calm and agree first. It is easier for me to follow the rules now because I know I agreed on the rule and on the consequence if I do not follow the rule."
msgstr ""
"Mama na Baba yangu mara nyingi waliniadhibu pindi walipokuwa na hasira na mimi. Walinifokea na mimi nilipata hasira. Mara nyingi sikufuata sheria zao, kwa sababu zilikuwa kali, sikuelewa kile walichokuwa wakisema, au Nilikuwa sijihangaishi kuwasikiliza, kwa sababu wote tulikuwa na hasira.\n"
"\n"
"Siku moja, waliniuliza: Hebu tufikiri kwa pamoja madhara yanayoweza kukupata kwa kushindwa kurudi nyumbani kwa wakati. Ilikuwa ni furaha kubwa kutoa maoni yangu kabla kitu hakijatokea na kutufanya wote kuwa na hasira. Wote tulitulia na kukubaliana kwanza. Sasa ni rahisi kwangu kufuata sheria kwa sababu najua na nilikubali sheria hizo na madhara kama sitafuata sheria hizo."

